  "logNo": "224216959734",
  "title": "식품 박스 제작에서 가장 많이 사용되는 유형과 단가 절감 방법",
  "addDate": "2026. 3. 20.",
  "categoryNo": "63",
  "url": "https://m.blog.naver.com/cookthedesign/224216959734",
  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-88613214-bfd4-4763-b4cc-a259fdf86d9c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-496ca037-2ed8-427b-bfd2-7cfe703b72eb\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-571ef227-60d5-4054-be81-27771a796dd0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">안녕하세요. (주)파파스컴퍼니입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-84a41f90-bae8-45fc-8211-38eaced971d1\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c9932940-06a2-4288-a272-3ae5ed33660c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-da2cc0b8-7231-4b59-80a3-75b8424e4912\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7da0f878-07a0-48a1-a88c-4634d9555085\" style=\"color:#555555;\">식품 패키지 박스는 단순히 제품을 담는 것을 넘어, 위생과 신선도 그리고 브랜드의 첫인상을 결정하는 핵심 요소입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0bf67771-e619-4ed5-ba3c-47436fb8bc0d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d8cbe1fb-aaa2-4886-b858-5227c8b6b3a3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">30년 차 인쇄 전문가의 시선으로 정리한 식품 박스의 주요 유형과 2026년 최신 트렌드를 블로그 포스팅 형식으로 정리해 드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-98315f05-1106-451e-87d3-ecd01c726e22\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:850px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-98315f05-1106-451e-87d3-ecd01c726e22\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNjAzMTRfMTMg/MDAxNzczNDgxNDA4MzE5.mi-VyXPVrfkPUHhGKsmOeI2itm4XGb1Yf136eAMNrbQg.623-Mn-vAgdRKBrcvFx3xFD3UHdkwMJJ90llaANjCHEg.PNG/%EC%8B%9D%ED%92%88%EB%8B%A8%EC%83%81%EC%9E%90_001.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"850\", \"originalHeight\" : \"595\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\", \"fileSize\": \"421594\" }' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNjAzMTRfMTMg/MDAxNzczNDgxNDA4MzE5.mi-VyXPVrfkPUHhGKsmOeI2itm4XGb1Yf136eAMNrbQg.623-Mn-vAgdRKBrcvFx3xFD3UHdkwMJJ90llaANjCHEg.PNG/%EC%8B%9D%ED%92%88%EB%8B%A8%EC%83%81%EC%9E%90_001.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e162aada-20c4-4507-a61d-7defb9f11d50\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9985d11c-1c08-4a56-8754-ad97aa81a492\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-145b170f-fcbe-49fb-b8ce-40867aeb16da\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-347fc636-7524-4c2b-94ec-208ae097c853\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-45d8535c-ae31-49d5-8e8c-26f2e7e7835d\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>■ 식품 박스, 가장 많이 사용되는 3가지 유형</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c3299583-91de-4ecf-bb3f-a37e68e2d6c1\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0d429193-a7c9-4b1c-b632-3e230f3ba57e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">식품의 특성(무게, 수분, 온도)에 따라 가장 대중적으로 쓰이는 형태는 다음과 같습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9ea69ef9-6e1e-4382-826b-bd69293de764\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3dd7c749-773c-4e1f-85bf-8988f1e41907\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-72e4ba02-26ff-4b8a-9c9a-50898cd01057\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-6626a33d-a791-4ebe-bdf4-43df89a4c265\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>1. 단상자 (Folding Carton)</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e7818969-6920-4537-b950-bce46962ce5e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-c8b043be-b9ac-4f8f-b9e5-159025624d39\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>· 특징</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cdc4a7da-8c33-40a2-864d-a8a380bbcde2\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 하나의 종이 판재를 접어서 만드는 가장 기본적인 형태입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8fb329b9-114c-4b3e-a61d-25be4bce333b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c55f24d0-9d54-4015-b5f2-59ba8604db3c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3b60df2a-65f6-4b8c-9cfc-fc271e3debeb\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-80471401-afc6-4cb2-9b9a-7e602350f740\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>· 종류</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-db45cf7d-ba6c-4a8b-9b93-ac8fa6be9bb3\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : B형은 위아래 입구가 똑같은 형태로, 가벼운 과자나 차(Tea) 박스에 주로 쓰입니다. 편의점에 있는 과자상자 박스를 생각하시면 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7b4039e9-4dbb-413a-b27d-0e93123133f9\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:550px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-7b4039e9-4dbb-413a-b27d-0e93123133f9\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNjAzMTRfMjM3/MDAxNzczNDgxNjYwNzc5.5xZZMuWZ_s9qF0oa-2Qxw2tamArx5riHpxLBPpOg_4Mg.Xhi7uEbXfQneXR207vT53MugRbEROvLs7zIlyuM1ekkg.JPEG/SE-7b4039e9-4dbb-413a-b27d-0e93123133f9.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"566\", \"originalHeight\" : \"566\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\", \"fileSize\": \"142042\" }' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNjAzMTRfMjM3/MDAxNzczNDgxNjYwNzc5.5xZZMuWZ_s9qF0oa-2Qxw2tamArx5riHpxLBPpOg_4Mg.Xhi7uEbXfQneXR207vT53MugRbEROvLs7zIlyuM1ekkg.JPEG/SE-7b4039e9-4dbb-413a-b27d-0e93123133f9.jpg?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-84aeaa24-fdae-43a5-9e3d-6814a760c6a0\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-25bbd88b-6167-4870-b228-2bdbe12d3ac6\" style=\"\">롯데 과자 캡처</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3623dd9d-cd40-49be-8d6b-4abb4b182c58\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f10d9147-add7-4569-8db3-11da70fd3774\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8e52cc32-9053-4961-b3a6-439a17642ac6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">맞뚜껑처럼 만들 수도 있고 십자형/원터치 바닥(삼면접착형)등 바닥면을 보강하여 햇반, 밀키트 등 무게감이 있는 식품에 적합합니다. 이런 단상자는 무게가 비교적 가볍고 단가가 중요한 소비재 제품이거나 고급스러움보다는 경제적 측면이 강한 제품일 때 많이 사용됩니다. 아래 설명하는 G형 박스나 슬리브 박스보다는 저렴한 형태의 박스입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2c92a38c-fc2c-4844-ae73-46a8aa57ebce\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bc1db44f-a202-40c4-b387-098cb35d014c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e65410c1-640f-4192-b570-9f8fb8719f43\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-07f5730e-1848-49e1-bc57-aeae5096f0bf\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>· 용도</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-57505708-8daa-432e-a40e-360a7cc2b06d\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 제과, 제빵, 건강기능식품, 소포장 간편식 등.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d25788a5-0f2f-425a-bb57-dbcdc700a058\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0e7e1b61-89ea-4195-8c2d-de3918c0caab\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5dc543ba-b962-4fe5-ae0f-3f21fa4a4786\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ff454efa-1317-412d-a0c3-d7338a4cf85f\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>2. 골판지 합지 박스 (Corrugated Box)</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2ce93d7a-5f7b-44ac-8be5-3825d8d96e18\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-edbea136-48ef-42ed-890b-2a26ed0e5281\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>· 특징</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-67fac43a-f883-4b3d-9232-dd251debcdbf\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 일반 종이(마닐라지 등)에 골판지를 붙여(합지) 내구성을 극대화한 박스입니다. 물론 가벼운 제품의 경우에는 골판지 합지가 아닌 단상자 형태의 G형 박스로도 제작이 가능합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-imageGroup se-l-slide\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-extend\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-imageGroup se-l-slide\" id=\"SE-402450be-7876-49e9-bd07-7a6d64d42ea7\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-viewer\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-container\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-0e473eff-d431-46ca-901d-4e1474790229\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNjAzMTVfNDMg/MDAxNzczNTQwMDc2MDQ0.VtNFmeDhePUZNYdLsiCR3cbw7_XUeeflJUTwjlW-dRAg.gAiwYOmZ6Gd16EI4xny-KgSbfMX4b4txBahncITJT-wg.PNG/%EC%8B%9D%ED%92%88%EB%8B%A8%EC%83%81%EC%9E%90_003.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"708\", \"originalHeight\" : \"595\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\", \"fileSize\": \"667792\" }' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNjAzMTVfNDMg/MDAxNzczNTQwMDc2MDQ0.VtNFmeDhePUZNYdLsiCR3cbw7_XUeeflJUTwjlW-dRAg.gAiwYOmZ6Gd16EI4xny-KgSbfMX4b4txBahncITJT-wg.PNG/%EC%8B%9D%ED%92%88%EB%8B%A8%EC%83%81%EC%9E%90_003.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-6959c14c-03d5-4744-ad60-1600370e5da0\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNjAzMTVfNTEg/MDAxNzczNTQwMDc2MDAz.SVPsI6KR1vczyVZp3yt-DNM_f9S374Nym3dQbXHcZI4g.81KQXFNnWQWKxtl8xJ-6UrID0Eu_2stj2TL8wQ1JQwAg.PNG/%EC%8B%9D%ED%92%88%EB%8B%A8%EC%83%81%EC%9E%90_004.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"822\", \"originalHeight\" : \"595\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\", \"fileSize\": \"648663\" }' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" c