ontent\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8872e212-0c85-43d2-adee-40a284c281c4\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-1a391480-8f9b-443e-a582-a717c1420d8b\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-01925c4a-4d12-4485-b29e-60fae0fc8e5e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-fd6967e1-2df8-4ee7-98f7-1c01b095a9c2\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>3. 슬리브형 박스 (Sleeve Box)</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-542214e1-c6e1-4685-9f4b-ec7601b80bc7\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-6797421a-9aed-4255-bd1a-5d6dbed69d01\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>· 특징</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7bc6365d-2a6f-42da-9755-69996ab38f36\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 내부 상자를 겉면에 띠지 형태의 슬리브로 감싸는 방식입니다. 가장 고급스럽고 2중으로 제품을 보호하면서 슬리브를 열 때의 고객의 감각적인 자극도 추구할 수 있는 형태입니다. 윗면에 창문 무양을 넣어서 제품이 보이도록 만들 수도 있고 여러 가지 변형된 형태로도 작업이 가능합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-54761936-0381-4979-b332-d72a04a31cea\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-54761936-0381-4979-b332-d72a04a31cea\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNjAzMTVfMjY0/MDAxNzczNTM5MTQ5NDQ3.Mze7aqVKbfsK1ptq-m43fGc2x1tL96SScpP5uoGE214g.QGe3qOEEGwAw-Ebk-qqMY8Y3Xp3Rmuv4hNoRpK8XNB0g.PNG/%EC%8B%9D%ED%92%88%EB%8B%A8%EC%83%81%EC%9E%90_002.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"992\", \"originalHeight\" : \"595\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\", \"fileSize\": \"673804\" }' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNjAzMTVfMjY0/MDAxNzczNTM5MTQ5NDQ3.Mze7aqVKbfsK1ptq-m43fGc2x1tL96SScpP5uoGE214g.QGe3qOEEGwAw-Ebk-qqMY8Y3Xp3Rmuv4hNoRpK8XNB0g.PNG/%EC%8B%9D%ED%92%88%EB%8B%A8%EC%83%81%EC%9E%90_002.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8fcaa3cb-0511-4c98-a7e6-5544cbc1be0a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9b2e404f-aacf-4205-a8b0-65bad7f479f5\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e62cfef9-d259-4522-baa6-47326a53f96e\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>· 장점</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-926567c7-fc7e-40ee-9af8-dd878a985a75\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 제품의 전면을 다 가리지 않아 내용물을 부분적으로 보여줄 수 있고, 고급스러운 느낌을 줍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-134e2149-2f27-4057-95f1-729f17462858\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4650e936-cb3e-4927-b601-46118b34ab75\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9433e9ea-51e4-4bae-b2ab-7f238dda5897\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-546a4952-7577-4884-b74b-7d47ab9ddd90\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>· 용도</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-d5e65bc8-f6df-4f58-b8b1-efd6b8f6d2aa\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b835be14-f385-4a1a-a992-f1be4920ee6e\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 프리미엄 디저트, 고가 도시락, 한정판 식품 패키지.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b0845f54-6f29-4267-832d-a835d6cb72c3\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f0d4bc5c-0706-4428-9e95-83a338144306\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><a class=\"se-link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\": \"SE-f0d4bc5c-0706-4428-9e95-83a338144306\", \"link\": \"https://blog.naver.com/cookthedesign/224101049811\"}' data-linktype=\"text\" href=\"https://blog.naver.com/cookthedesign/224101049811\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.naver.com/(주)파파스컴퍼니/224101049811</a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> \n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9f71588e-1b03-4991-9ad0-b7d03c7ae09e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c1c6dbb7-b316-4ab8-a90b-b5efc5444b86\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7c96511d-c302-401d-ab6b-0efe01bc7d4a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-735b427a-c2b4-4c53-991a-a002eb4603c9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-04ecafeb-385f-41e1-851f-af366f3041f8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8d1419c5-bbbc-4b54-85d3-e11e1583f323\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2d66f73e-b075-44e0-8c28-d6cfe74e01f6\" style=\"color:#36851e;\">🌿 2026 식품 패키지 핵심 트렌드</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4886ba6c-53de-4b19-9e1e-5aada0cbbd05\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2b337bb5-4e64-4ad6-afcf-fc358c7aac04\" style=\"color:#555555;\">올해 식품 업계의 패키징 키워드는 '</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-79df46f9-36c5-4680-b44d-c952d885abed\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>입증된 지속가능성</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b8dbcba0-1c8c-4b4b-827c-b393ec2e1164\" style=\"color:#555555;\">'과 '</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-9a58ca77-e331-4ed5-9325-14af5b0c4c46\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>디지털 연결성</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-71319597-168c-4865-9390-93540db8259c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">'입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0f3376ae-9271-4e63-aeaf-4fbb1db61ed1\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9d6ecb02-504a-4275-9c9a-139ce07fa448\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ae8b9027-f0f7-48fb-98e9-166f17e72d95\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-a9370289-3016-4850-9249-77593f098e7b\" style=\"color:#36851e;\"><b>1. \"지속가능성\"의 구체화 (PPWR 대응)</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9fc9f8da-e642-469d-b03e-847813fb9320\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f4d1ed17-882e-48c6-b0cc-e99734ed2035\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이제 단순히 \"친환경 종이\"라고 말하는 것만으로는 부족합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6c58a47e-16c6-4bd4-9946-f715b017533c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-99f26ab8-3d78-4014-a422-8930a269b057\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7efe8df1-366c-41af-b13b-afc37b5a4a04\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-023197bb-98a0-4a7c-8f78-9b679755b45e\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>단일 소재(Mono-material)</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6b41eb80-b0af-40b7-b656-81bd31fd26d8\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 재활용이 쉽도록 비닐 코팅을 제거하거나, 종이와 플라스틱이 자연스럽게 분리되는 구조가 필수입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-701c1898-6793-4e5b-9c6b-96da346703d8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-aae82474-5331-4562-a87b-4ce3f4a0be8c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e4a249b8-cd41-4e91-ac54-fee53d297c35\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-2a4f1e9b-97e3-430f-b29d-abc5ca5fff20\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>탈(脫) 플라스틱</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1f85e92c-29bd-40b0-a419-82c5631f0347\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 기존의 플라스틱 트레이를 대체하는 펄프 몰드나 바이오 소재 기반의 종이 용기 도입이 중소기업까지 확산되고 있습니다. 이런 이유로 내부 패드가 게또바시(?)는 점점 줄어드는 추세입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-20c9ce2a-7b46-450c-9346-07830ef39d55\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-20c9ce2a-7b46-450c-9346-07830ef39d55\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNjAzMTVfMTg4/MDAxNzczNTQwMjE1MjI1.vO-ufwWhDfcFc2bysGVedFDqZiZr7S9Rje9tSyhdXZkg.a