t\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5d47f248-7f9e-4195-83e4-b41ecdf871ae\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3c2bcee1-0a56-406e-8cf3-2fe9bda1f3e7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c255989c-28d9-4725-a906-1e43d7dc6a6a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-9bc45ea5-d286-4440-9ec1-733d08c7b955\" style=\"color:#36851e;\"><b>2. 스마트 패키징 (QR &amp; AR)</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2847a710-0567-45f4-8b4d-9b4ec4d863c8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-db0b85b7-0eba-467d-933f-7e86144ee8d1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">패키지가 단순한 포장이 아닌 '정보 전달 매체'로 진화하고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-91e7d797-76c4-4176-ae76-915827af0e0b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cb8190a4-4859-4d51-b1fd-374c0f604b01\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b6a50faa-11da-4865-8bd8-bdb696c766bc\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-0fe84f44-634a-444d-9f05-bb8996db6095\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>QR 코드의 필수화</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1af482eb-aad9-4780-8c8a-2e0a11f50d99\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 원산지 정보, 조리법(레시피), 생산 이력을 QR 하나로 연결합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ae197890-e067-4bc5-b3dd-d1fdcea0dff0\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6775eb09-026c-44d5-a8ac-4c1aa40a7793\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c5310def-72f9-4cc4-920a-79f40c76a80b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ca018d1b-2ce4-4da3-a932-5d97f395afaa\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>인터랙티브 경험</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f23d5786-8c80-4888-a989-b6f578d73d79\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 스마트폰을 가져다 대면 브랜드 스토리가 나오는 AR 기술이 적용되어 소비자에게 신뢰와 재미를 동시에 제공합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4c011e11-e2fd-4dc4-8ef5-9f88750a4c69\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2529fc96-d785-496b-a337-b5a4e3f5b71f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ab1be83c-c319-4594-ae4a-40f8dc66b6c2\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ddaefa07-3389-4b3a-89ac-3f3ae734ae2a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-085f8c16-737c-430e-b80c-059378aa7b6d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-af7a05ec-cb90-49c7-9897-242170a75a22\" style=\"color:#36851e;\"><b>3. 어스 톤(Earth Tone)과 질감 디자인</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4ac86e43-ac3d-48f3-ae4a-fc88d033aae2\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3f535bee-87b2-45a8-a799-dd954de853cc\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>시각적 신뢰</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-29c3985e-35e9-4f9c-bc7e-7db5e3f6b578\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 화려한 원색보다는 테라코타, 이끼색, 흙빛 등 자연에서 온 어스 팔레트가 대세입니다. 이런 이유로 크라프트지가 많이 사용되고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-51615e03-470a-42b0-82d5-0e35f2cff1b9\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-51615e03-470a-42b0-82d5-0e35f2cff1b9\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNjAzMTVfMjg5/MDAxNzczNTQwMzE1ODI0.5saQKbZrywe8o-7Xzesg7R0ycjOMz49JnaJb44u9k_Ig.kHAVxjh-hWqY3_9tX5cH-zjy-saheTuOmxvSOeN9rZIg.PNG/Gemini_Generated_Image_40dbs540dbs540db.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"2816\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1536\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\", \"fileSize\": \"7588676\" }' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNjAzMTVfMjg5/MDAxNzczNTQwMzE1ODI0.5saQKbZrywe8o-7Xzesg7R0ycjOMz49JnaJb44u9k_Ig.kHAVxjh-hWqY3_9tX5cH-zjy-saheTuOmxvSOeN9rZIg.PNG/Gemini_Generated_Image_40dbs540dbs540db.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-032b5225-3c63-44ed-933d-0c2e23db099d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d101ed68-90e2-400f-b7ca-155a2ab327be\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-03e01300-fc7a-4be0-92de-f462ee9e4bc2\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>촉각적 마케팅</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-504e96af-4bae-424a-a8d6-01a87d8f9743\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 비코팅지나 재생지의 거친 질감을 그대로 살려 \"이 제품은 건강하고 정직하다\"라는 메시지를 시각뿐 아니라 촉각으로도 전달합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-732b6588-758a-4e28-b682-e4f1e606b38f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f8c1b85d-165b-462b-b371-9c52f0472e2f\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-12deda3a-bcaf-47ee-be5c-63394216a955\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6ba64ee0-f1a8-42cf-9d9c-5f4ce4472cc0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f65d1089-9e46-4b79-9428-a1b133bb1b99\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-1b9a3dd2-5c7f-4041-9791-2aa51cd8e3be\" style=\"color:#36851e;\"><b>4. 실버 경제를 고려한 \"포용적 디자인\"</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-63997a6c-70f3-4e88-b8e0-9826fde47c59\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ef1df41e-7d87-4695-80f4-d4d4a1d0700f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">손에 힘이 없는 고령층도 쉽게 뜯을 수 있는 이지 오픈(Easy-open) 구조와 가독성이 높은 큰 타이포그래피가 프리미엄 식품군에서 중요한 설계 요소로 자리 잡았습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-57ca3593-2aac-4f82-8aaa-4d807d8cab62\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9d6cbad4-21d5-4c2b-a8c1-dcda8ea7596b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5d3271ca-e115-4724-9b4c-6e82e23b551c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d877dbee-c55f-4823-805a-3a4b7003e8f9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니 블로그 이웃분들 중에서 특정 식품(예 : 냉동식품, 와인 등)에 최적화된 도면이나 재질 추천이 필요하시면 언제든 문의나 홈페이지 댓글 남겨주세요!</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-54ec8a86-9e88-44c8-afe1-59097df3a7d9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-954a8d81-97b9-4a76-a173-a40ee8baa0a9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5d3d929c-403f-471c-b52d-4cdca617d3b9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1d20cdea-12fb-4075-9988-aa9e38c673ce\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-53910440-e932-4d17-80ef-bd87a85f4fb8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n<a class=\"se-module se-module-talktalk\" href=\"https://talk.naver.com/w4tbeb?frm=mblog&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fm.blog.naver.com%2Fcookthedesign%2F224216959734#nafullscreen\" onclick=\"sendClickNlog('pst.talktalk', '');\">\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
